    "description": "VMware India, one of India's leading organizations, is hiring a Software Engineer for our Jabalpur operations. We offer a competitive salary package along with world-class benefits.\n\nAbout VMware India:\nVMware India is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Mentor junior developers and conduct knowledge-sharing sessions\n• Participate in code reviews and contribute to technical discussions\n• Ensure code security and follow best practices for data protection\n• Deploy and manage applications on cloud platforms like AWS, Azure, or GCP\n• Write clean, maintainable, and well-documented code\n• Contribute to system architecture and technical design decisions\n• Work with agile methodologies including daily stand-ups and sprint planning\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Chartered Accountant (ICAI)\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in React\n• Proficiency in Python\n• Proficiency in Kubernetes\n• Proficiency in JavaScript\n• Proficiency in REST APIs\n• Proficiency in Git\n• Proficiency in Docker\n• Proficiency in Java\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Jabalpur, Madhya Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with VMware India!",
